snippet.description:
I started this activation off with a Bone Headed move.  I muted my audio. But a quite voice over fixed the problem.  I've wanted to activate Clark Creek Natural Area in Pond, MS for some time and I finally got it done.  The contacts were fast and I had to leave some Hunters hanging on the frequency.  I'll definitely get back up there in hopes of putting the park in more Hunter logs.
